The tested device (DUT) is a BGP route reflector for the VPNv4 addres family
It runs OSPF with the P-router and exchanges VPNv4 prefixes with PE-routers.
The validation tests check VRF IPv4 prefixes on the PE-routers and perform end-to-end connectivity tests.
